title: Need Immediately!  Need a ClickFunnels expert to grab an existing page and import it into my ClickFunnels account.
snippet: I will give you a one page site that already is being used on another person's clickfunnels account.  I just need you to copy it and put it into my account.  I don't know the person that owns the original page, hence I'm not able to ask them to "send/share" the template with me.  I need you to quickly recreate the template.
